description:
When experience matters, schedule a free consultation at the Howell, New Jersey, office of Levinson Axelrod, P.A. Our staff of dedicated professionals will thoroughly examine your case and provide legal feedback and insight regarding your options for monetary recovery.

We offer 100 percent FREE case evaluations to help determine if you have sufficient grounds to file a lawsuit, and we only get paid if we win your case.

The New Jersey personal injury lawyers at Levinson Axelrod, P.A., are prepared to handle a wide range of cases, including:

  • Motor vehicle accidents, including car accidents, truck accidents and motorcycle accidents
  • Dog bites
  • Faulty pharmaceutical products
  • Medical malpractice
  • Premises liability
  • Product liability
  • Workers' compensation
  • Wrongful death

Additionally, our firm is regularly called upon to provide legal guidance to clients in professional malpractice cases, consumer fraud cases and class-action lawsuits. Contact us to learn more about how we can help.

Celebrating 80 years of practice.

By fighting to recover compensation for lost wages, medical bills, property damage, and pain and suffering, we can help protect our clients' financial future. Let us focus on negotiating with the at-fault party's insurance carrier — you focus on returning to a pre-accident health.

Contact our law firm to schedule a free consultation and receive an honest case evaluation. We maintain seven area offices for the convenience of our clients.
